<i>noun</i>: 셔츠 [], 남방 [남방] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>셔츠 []</dt><br>
<dd>shirt</dd><br>
<dd>양복 안에 받쳐 입거나 겉옷으로 입는 서양식 윗옷.</dd><br>
<dd>A western upper garment worn inside a suit or as an outer clothing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>남방 [남방]</dt><br>
<dd>1. south</dd><br>
<dd>동서남북 중 남의 방향.</dd><br>
<dd>The south, one of the four cardinal directions.</dd><br>
<dd>2. south</dd><br>
<dd>남쪽 지방.</dd><br>
<dd>A southern region.</dd><br>
<dd>3. shirt</dd><br>
<dd>칼라가 달려 있으며 앞 부분의 단추를 채워 입는 셔츠.</dd><br>
<dd>A shirt with collars worn by fastening the buttons on the front.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>